From 9fb6bb5f560e507d5eef7a76cf6a3ab14a91d2d7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Munya Kanaventi <mkanaventi@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 06:57:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add LLM-powered Academy module

- Netlify serverless function (llm.js) proxying to Anthropic Claude API
  with 4 modes: scenario simulation, Socratic tutor, practice quiz,
  report review
- Academy dashboard with domain overview and quick-launch tools
- AI Scenario Simulator with 4-axis scoring (safety, boundaries,
  documentation, de-escalation)
- Socratic AI Tutor with conversation starters and chat interface
- Practice Assessment with adaptive question generation and scoring
- Academy CSS extending Mercury design system
- Routes and navigation for all roles (monitors + owners)
- Database migration for progress tracking tables with RLS policies
- Build verified: 130 modules, 0 errors
